7. Our results confirm the\nhypothesis of a high degree of heterogeneity yielding very different pricing\nstrategies over distinct municipalities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 8 Nov 2020 15:07:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 8 Apr 2021 12:27:40 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 10 Jan 2022 21:33:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-12"}
